ange of cleat positioning to suit evolving preferences. </p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.crankbrothers.com/search?type=product%2Carticle%2Cpage%2Ccollection&amp;options[prefix]=last&amp;q=candy%20lace*\" target=\"_blank\">Crankbrothers</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/crankbrothers-candy-lace-shoes/\">Crankbrothers Candy Lace Shoes</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"4c5abc1887628a8db63ea076e0f896f22724162ef81cc47d4c6557ff25e80c0e","category":"Cycling"}